ct/131482/', '', 'Atorvastatin, Simvastatin, Lovastatin, Rosuvastatin, Niacin, Pravastatin, Ezetimibe, Bempedoic acid, Fenofibrate', 'Fluocinolone acetonide, Fluorometholone', 1767369485);
